subject: Re: [Read_Alphabet] Is this group defunct?
msgSnippet: I would second Nathan s request that you share these early letters with the group.  Especially the ones from Read himself.  I received a brief letter from Read
messageBody: I would second Nathan's request that you share these early letters with the group.  Especially the ones from Read himself.  I received a brief letter from Read at one time, but I have no idea where it is now.  In it he advised me of the development of QS.  I had run across a copy of Androcles and the Lion in Shavian and TO and had written to Sir James Pitman asking for more information.  He forwarded my letter to KR.
